In the INTEREST OF K.P., K.P., J.P., K.P., J.P., K.P., J.P., and K.P., Minor Children, K.P., Mother, Appellant, B.S., Father of K.P., Appellant. No. 19-0470 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed June 19, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

A mother and the father of one of her children appeal the juvenile court's removal order in a child-in-need-of-assistance proceeding. REVERSED IN PART AND REMANDED.

REVERSED IN PART AND REMANDED.
